{"word":"G5463 - χαίρω - chaírō - khah'-ee-ro - Farewell","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χαίρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chaírō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khah'-ee-ro</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Farewell</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சந்தோஷமடை, சந்தோஷப்படு, களிகூர், மகிழ், வாழ்த்து"},{"paragraph":"to rejoice, be glad"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to be full of <i>&ldquo;cheer&rdquo;</i>, that is, calmly <i>happy</i> or well off; impersonal especially as a salutation (on meeting or parting), <i>be well:</i> - farewell, be glad, God speed, greeting, hail, joy (-fully), rejoice.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2168/2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169/2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170/2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796/4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463/5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479/5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483/5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484/5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485/5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486/5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487/5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884/884\">G884</a>"}]}